Requirements:
	python-twitter 0.8
	oauth2 1.2.0

Examples:
	post status
		ptwit post hello world
	get public timeline
		ptwit public
	get mentions
		ptwit mentions
	send message:
		ptwit send someone hello, ptwit is awesome

Usage: ptwit [COMMAND | PAGE]

Available commands:
    public
    mention[s]  [PAGE]
    repl[y,ies] [PAGE]
	message[s]
    post        MESSAGE
    friend[s]
    follower[s]
    favorite[s] [USER] [PAGE]
    status      [USER] [PAGE]
    send        USER MESSAGE
    search      TERM
    rate
    help
